data.description: THE RETREAT, Pulte's Patio Home neighborhood at Sunbury Meadows. Rare when one comes to market. This 'Move-In Ready' 2 BR, 2 Bath, 1,662 SF, popular Open Floor Plan shows like NEW. Upgrades throughout! Fixtures, Back Splash, Ceiling Fans, LVT in a earth tone palette. Mega Kitchen with acres of Counters, oodles of 'soft-close' Wood Cabinets with pull out drawers. S/S Appliances includes French Door Refrigerator, 5 burner Gas Range and Dishwasher & Microwave. 'Dine At' Island with room to entertain family and friends who like to hang there. Great Room with Gas Log Fireplace. Leads to concrete Patio with GAZEBO!  Large Primary En Suite with Dual Sinks, Shower for 2, big Walk-In Closet. 1st Floor Laundry, 2.5 car Garage, alarm system. AWESOME COMMUNITY POOL! HOA cares for landscape and snow.
